5 Thank you to each and every person who supported me, donated to our campaign, hosted events and yard signs, sent me encouraging cards…these memories will stay with me forever. 💙

4 It was the great honor of my life to serve on the Baxter City Council, and be the DFL nominee for the MN House and US House. We made history together when I was named the nominee for CD8. I may have been the first, but I’ll work hard to make sure I’m not the last.
